{"tid":631111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日食sushi入黎","createTime":"2018-04-16T07:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T08:24:22.000Z","uid":181666,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04bd86d6016b4120c9be29b7f63c2fb1942cef5f","tid":631111,"uid":181666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T07:31:14.000Z","msg":"海魚相比起淡水魚少寄生蟲，<br />\n但係唔代表佢冇寄生蟲。<br />\n點解好似冇咩人討論過魚係咪可以生食，<br />\n係google youtube search 都冇咩講，<br />\n大多數都focus係點食魚生果d，<br />\n其實大家有冇擔心過食魚生會出問題，<br />\ne.g. 身體差左/病既次數多左。<br />\n其實每年都有新聞講人體取出寄生蟲，只係唔多所以好快沉左。<br />\n雖然我都有食魚生，但發覺冇咩報導/source證明佢係安全，又仲好多人食。<br />\n純屬想討論下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecf588d1dc0bf57abf6608124e2f527cd42cf89","tid":631111,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d4143cdafe1018c325512be5be22dff87770dd9","tid":631111,"uid":149151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T08:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}